with RSA-2048 key generation, RS256 token signing, K8s Secret persistence (`picod-router-identity`) |\n| `backend.go` | `Backend` struct + `BackendHealthChecker` with consecutive fail/success thresholds |\n| `loadbalancer.go` | `LoadBalancer` interface; `RoundRobinBalancer` and `LeastConnectionsBalancer` implementations |\n| `middleware.go` | `ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware` (semaphore via buffered channel), `RequestLoggerMiddleware`, `TraceIDMiddleware` |\n| `router.go` | `Router` interface (`AddRoute`, `RemoveRoute`, `ServeHTTP`) + `routerImpl` with `sync.RWMutex`-protected route map |\n| `informer.go` | `InformerManager` using `SharedInformerFactory` to watch AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs (event handlers are currently stubs logging at V(4)) |\n| `health.go` | `/health/live` and `/health/ready` endpoints |\n| `errors.go` | `SessionNotFoundError` and `SandboxTemplateNotFoundError` custom error types |\n\n---\n\n### 3. Spec and Design Files\n\n**Root-level spec files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` -- AR-009 Router HTTP reverse proxy core delta spec (821 lines, Chinese, highly detailed with Gherkin scenarios)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` -- Test specification\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` -- AR-009 Router design (411 lines, Chinese)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` -- AR-010 Router session management proposal (234 lines, Chinese)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` -- Project context overview\n\n**Per-module spec files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/spec.md` -- Session routing spec (115 lines, English)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/spec.md` -- Session store spec (118 lines, English)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/code-execution/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/spec.md`\n\n**Per-change delta-spec files:**\n- `changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md`\n- `changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md`\n- `changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md`\n- `changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md`\n- `changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md`\n- `changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md`\n\n---\n\n### 4. CRD Types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n\n**Files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n\n#### AgentRuntime Type\n\n```go\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ObjectMeta\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort        // target ports with path prefix, name, port, protocol\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate    // Pod template (labels, annotations, corev1.PodSpec)\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration    // idle timeout\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration    // TTL\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n}\n```\n\n#### CodeInterpreter Type\n\n```go\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=codeinterpreters\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ObjectMeta\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate  // image, env, command, args, resources, runtimeClassName\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32          // if > 0, creates SandboxClaim instead of Sandbox\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType    // \"picod\" or \"none\"\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n    Ready      bool\n}\n```\n\n#### Shared Types\n\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string  // \"HTTP\" or \"HTTPS\"\ntype AuthModeType string  // \"picod\" or \"none\"\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string\n    Name       string\n    Port       uint32\n    Protocol   ProtocolType\n}\n```\n\n#### Kind Constants (from `pkg/common/types/types.go`)\n\n```go\nconst (\n    AgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    CodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    SandboxKind         = \"Sandbox\"\n    SandboxClaimKind    = \"SandboxClaim\"\n)\n```\n\n#### GVR Constants (from `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go`)\n\n```go\nAgentRuntimeGVR    = runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/agentruntimes\nCodeInterpreterGVR = runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/codeinterpreters\nSandboxGVR         = agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes\nSandboxClaimGVR    = extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Existing Router-Related Code Patterns\n\nThe `pkg/router` module is a fully structured HTTP reverse proxy with these patterns:\n\n**Server Architecture:**\n- Gin-based HTTP server with h2c (HTTP/2 cleartext) support\n- Routes registered under `/v1` group with middleware (logger, recovery, concurrency limit)\n- Health endpoints (`/health/live`, `/health/ready`) outside middleware\n\n**Route Registration:**\n```\nGET  /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path  -> handleAgentInvoke\nPOST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path  -> handleAgentInvoke\nGET  /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path -> handleCodeInterpreterInvoke\nPOST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path -> handleCodeInterpreterInvoke\n```\n\n**Request Flow:**\n1. Extract `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n2. If sessionID present: look up `SandboxInfo` from store\n3. If sessionID empty: POST to WorkloadManager to create sandbox\n4. Select entry point from `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` by path prefix match\n5. Build reverse proxy to `protocol://endpoint`\n6. Inject JWT (for Sandbox/SandboxClaim kinds) into `Authorization` header\n7. Set forwarding headers (`X-Forwarded-Host`, `X-Forwarded-Proto`, `X-Forwarded-For`)\n8. Proxy request, set `x-agentcube-session-id` on response\n9. Update `LastActivityAt` twice (before and after proxy)\n\n**Informer Pattern (currently stubs):**\n- `InformerManager` watches AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs via `SharedInformerFactory`\n- Event handlers (`onAgentRuntimeAdded`, `onCodeInterpreterUpdated`, etc.) currently only log at V(4)\n- The `Router` interface (`AddRoute`/`RemoveRoute`) exists but is not yet wired into the informers\n\n**Load Balancing:**\n- `RoundRobinBalancer` -- thread-safe circular selection, skips unhealthy backends\n- `LeastConnectionsBalancer` -- uses `atomic.Int64` counters per backend URL\n\n**Health Checking:**\n- `BackendHealthChecker` with configurable interval, consecutive fail/success thresholds\n- Default health check: HTTP GET to `{backend.URL}/health`\n\n---\n\n### 6. Session Management Patterns\n\n**Store Interface** (`pkg/store/store.go` -- currently a stub returning `nil`):\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID string, info *SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID string, info *SandboxInfo) error\n    DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID string) error\n    GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID string) (*SandboxInfo, error)\n    ListSandboxes(ctx) (map[string]*SandboxInfo, error)\n    UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID string, lastActivityTime interface{}) error\n}\n```\n\n**SessionManager Interface** (`pkg/router/session_manager.go`):\n```go\ntype SessionManager interface {\n    GetSandboxBySession(ctx, sessionID, namespace, name, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n}\n```\n\n**SandboxInfo Model** (`pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models.go`):\n```go\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    SessionID      string\n    SandboxName    string\n    SandboxID      string\n    WorkloadName   string\n    Namespace      string\n    Kind           string\n    PodIP          string\n    EntryPoints    []EntryPoint  // {Path, Protocol, Endpoint}\n    CreatedAt      time.Time\n    ExpiresAt      time.Time\n    Status         string\n    LastActivityAt time.Time\n}\n```\n\n**Session Lifecycle in WorkloadManager Reconciler:**\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime.go` -- reconciles AgentRuntime CRs, manages session store entries on create/update/delete\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go` -- same for CodeInterpreter CRs\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/pod.go` -- updates PodIP in store when pod IP changes\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` -- GC for expired/idle sessions, orphan CR detection, ghost entry cleanup\n\n**Session Key Naming** (from session-store spec):\n- Primary key: `session:{sessionID}` (JSON document)\n- Expiry index: sorted set `session:expiry` (score = ExpiresAt Unix seconds)\n- Activity index: sorted set `session:last_activity` (score = last activity Unix seconds)\n\n**Session Resolution Flow:**\n1. Router reads `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n2. If non-empty: `store.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` -> returns `SandboxInfo` or `ErrNotFound` -> `SessionNotFoundError`\n3. If empty: POST to `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime` or `/v1/code-interpreter` -> creates sandbox -> returns `CreateSandboxResponse` with SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n\n---\n\n### 7. Key Observations\n\n1. **No `main.go` entry point exists** in the repository -- there is no `cmd/` directory in the glob results. The `cmd/router/main.go` is referenced in specs but not yet implemented.\n\n2. **The Store interface is a stub** -- `Storage()` returns `nil`. The Redis/Valkey backend implementation is specified but not yet coded.\n\n3. **Informer event handlers are stubs** -- they log at V(4) but do not actually update the route table or session cache.\n\n4. **The `Router` interface exists but is not wired** into the Server -- the Server uses direct `SessionManager` + reverse proxy rather than the generic `Router` + `LoadBalancer` pattern.\n\n5. **Two parallel Store interfaces exist** -- one in `pkg/store/store.go` (used by router) and one in `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go` (slightly different signatures).\n\n6. **The project follows an \"AR\" (AgentCube Request) change management system** with 10 tracked changes (AR-001 through AR-010), each with design, proposal, tasks, and sometimes delta-spec documents.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28861a571ffehhcc4VWttJQv4c","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775828359819,"end":1775828501989}}}}
